I"'<p>Configurable/Dimmable WiFi Lightswitch</p>
<ul>
<li>Cloud registered, Local API communication (both RESTful and TCP pushed events)</li>
<li>Motion Sensor</li>
<li>Energy Meter</li>
<li>RGB Glow Ring</li>
<li>Wifi &amp; Bluetooth connectivity</li>
<li>Phone Apps for iOS &amp; Android</li>
</ul>
<h2>Configuration</h2>
<p>To enable Plum Lightpad support, add the following lines to your <code>configuration.yaml</code> file:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
plum_lightpad:
  username: YOUR_CLOUD_USERNAME
  password: YOUR_CLOUD_PASSWORD
</code></pre>
<div class="config-vars">
  <h3><a class="title-link" name="configuration-variables" href="#configuration-variables"></a> Configuration Variables</h3>
  <dl class=''><dt><a class='title-link' name='username' href='#username'></a> username</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>Your Plum Cloud username.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='password' href='#password'></a> password</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>Your Plum Cloud password.</p>
</span></p></dd></dl>
</div>
